translations: v.打开；揭露（unclose 的过去分词）

phrs.translation: 开着的, 未闭合的未完的, 打开, 未结束的

sentences.sentence: He returned to room, and unclosed the plastics bags.
sentences.translation: 他回到屋内，拆开塑料袋子。

sentences.sentence: Virtual User script footprint of around 18mb if there are unclosed HTTP connections.
sentences.translation: 如果存在未关闭的HTTP连接，虚拟用户脚本占用了18 M的内存。

sentences.sentence: An unclosed HTML document that includes an HTML head tag and the first part of the body tag.
sentences.translation: 一个未闭合的HTML文档，包含了HTML head标签和body标签的第一部分内容。
